%h3
  Latest discussion
%ul
  - Post.latest(6).each do |post|
    %li
      = link_to post.topic.name, forum_topic_url(post.topic.forum, post.topic)
      %span.credit
        - if post.topic.page
          was commented upon by
        - elsif post.first?
          was started by
        - else
          was replied to by
        = post.reader.name
        = friendly_date(post.created_at)